{"tid":1403508,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地可唔可以正名做愛國者？","createTime":"2019-08-03T19:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T19:30:45.000Z","uid":218699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"006c19b0ebe0cca8713742f1c80cf8d40048dead","tid":1403508,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:24:04.000Z","msg":"唔好屌住 睇埋下面先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/爱国者_(美国革命)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%88%B1%E5%9B%BD%E8%80%85_%28%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%29&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvKxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=84cd46d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/爱国者_(美国革命)</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">牛津英語詞典中「愛國者」的第三個定義是「積極抵抗佔領他/她祖國的敵軍的人；一個抵抗運動的成員，自由鬥士。 最初用於指美國獨立戰爭中抵抗和與英國戰鬥的人。」</span><br />\n<br />\n其實國唔一定指強國 我地心中愛住呢個地方 香港唔係限死指一個地方 只要有香港人 有同路人 有有心人 就可以自成一個香港一個一國 <br />\n<br />\n其實愛國唔一定係貶義 反而可以成位文宣利器<br />\n因為示威者 抗爭者係文宣/tv上比人（老一輩）感覺上始終仲有有少少負面 /直接聯想搞事<br />\n但愛國者比班廢老一聽首先都會停一停諗一諗先 至少唔會第一下就聯想負面嘢<br />\n<br />\n試諗下tvb/直播入面啲記者係講<br />\n愛國者向xx地方推進<br />\n同<br />\n示威者向xx地方推進<br />\n中性詞即刻變正面詞<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得點？ 唔啱請屌細力啲 始終少出post 可能有少少膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd33c6be4b340018c96942d767fa4f4b8dad9700","tid":1403508,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd96754419440357f644d2a839964323f74775b","tid":1403508,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:26:16.000Z","msg":"去訓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日西區tko見<br />\n85仲有三罷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSx6qbt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSx6qbt.png&h=ce3d759c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"colo